## Noncommercial

Any use that is primarily intended for or directed toward commercial advantage
or private monetary compensation is not noncommercial. However, personal use
and use by individual hobbyists is noncommercial.

## No Other Rights

These terms do not allow you to sublicense or transfer any of your licenses to
